contents:
We have launched a new template gallery. In this gallery, you will find all Quiqr Community Templates. The templates are open source and free for everyone to use. The only thing you need is the Quiqr app, which you can also download for free.
The gallery is located at this location.
title: New Template Gallery

contents:
Quiqr went public at the Hugo Conf 2022. We want to thanks the people of the HugoConf for giving us time and space to promote our project.
  The slides of Pim’s Lightning Talk are available as a Quiqr Template.
title: Hugo Conf 2022
